abstract: Steve Reddicliffe reviews Colombian restaurant Aqui Es Santa Fe in Port Chester (Metropolitan/Westchester).

keywords.value: Aqui Es Santa Fe (Port Chester, NY, Restaurant)
keywords.name: organizations

lead_paragraph: Olga Santos labored for years before she could open a restaurant of her own. Today, she serves an impressive variety of delicious Colombian dishes, from ceviches to steak to a sweet corn cake dessert.
